title: Lichens on Wood
description: A close-up view of various lichens growing on a wooden surface. The image features vibrant yellow lichen with a textured surface, surrounded by lighter gray and white lichens, showcasing the diversity of colors and forms in these organisms.

title: Microscopic View of Mold
description: A close-up, microscopic image showing clusters of mold with a bluish hue, set against an orange background. The mold appears fuzzy, with a texture that suggests growth and reproduction.

title: Bacteria
description: A digital illustration of bacteria, showcasing a single bacterium in the foreground with a glowing outline and hair-like structures, set against a blurred blue background with additional bacteria in the distance.

title: Microscopic View of Algae and Microorganisms
description: An illustration depicting various green microorganisms, including elongated algae and spherical cells, set against a light background. The image showcases the diversity of microscopic life, highlighting the intricate shapes and textures of these organisms.

title: Underwater Scene with Kelp
description: A vibrant underwater scene showcasing lush green kelp swaying gently in the water. Sunlight filters through the surface, illuminating the kelp and creating a serene atmosphere.
